item.description:
Come join us for another unique Meet-Up with Maia, who is a psychic artist, who will connect with your energy, and draw a picture of what she "sees", which can include a past life, your higher self, or totem animal. Each 15 minute session includes a picture, and a psychic reading.
Each session is $33 per person.

You can check out her website, and spiritual art work at:

http://www.celebratey...

We will also be having a pot luck luncheon, and spiritual discussion group during the readings.

More info to come! :)
